{"tid":323651,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"自由哥講馬，18年睇馬經驗，你問我答 (16-07-2017沙田煞料日)","createTime":"2017-07-15T18:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T11:49:43.000Z","uid":113075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c76c3d573d09e74a573d742889aa09cd206ef4d","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係自由哥，歡迎大家問馬或者賽馬相關嘅問題，我會盡量為大家解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次煞料揀左兩隻心水，分別係第2場2號「馬飛龍」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7P1BfyqYlI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7P1BfyqYlI8&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b4ba629e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7P1BfyqYlI8</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋第8場6號「馬克羅斯」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15g2zLH3-kw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D15g2zLH3-kw&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e883bb19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15g2zLH3-kw</a>"},{"pid":"03c8991b4f954da2a8993f7b899a311d05eae213","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:14:50.000Z","msg":"另外，我揀左3場同大家重溫：<br />\n<br />\n今季令我O嘴嘅賽事第三位 - 歷險家誤撞傻雀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LdHEBXlCoJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLdHEBXlCoJg&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d187619a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LdHEBXlCoJg</a><br />\n<br />\n今季令我O嘴嘅賽事第二位 - 綽綽有餘慢閘跌鞭都贏馬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WA-WJBrbin4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWA-WJBrbin4&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4ee33521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WA-WJBrbin4</a><br />\n<br />\n今季令我O嘴嘅賽事第一位 - 雲呢拿大勝10個馬位<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ES-LFZQ3tic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DES-LFZQ3tic&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7372bd5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ES-LFZQ3tic</a><br />\n<br />\n自由哥YouTube channel：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDIyYbDdcPKifvni-I0NWgg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCDIyYbDdcPKifvni-I0NWgg&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=80c3c000\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDIyYbDdcPKifvni-I0NWgg</a><br />\n<br />\n自由哥fb專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spartanbn118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspartanbn118%2F&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7504866c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/spartanbn118/</a>"},{"pid":"4647de32d722ffa141e7514294c7bbeff2ebebd0","tid":323651,"uid":22501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e437e07af6a9e8eeb7cf09e4421a1714113acc3","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">你問我答回憶錄</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於馬</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>潘明輝：憑隻外型只睇到肌肉，但好多時馬既呼吸至係重點，你點睇？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：呼吸對隻馬確實好重要，條氣唔順自然唔會跑得快，正如人跑步一樣。至於點睇隻馬呼吸好唔好，老實講，作為一般馬迷好難有方法睇，聽一啲晨操派嘅評馬人講，佢地朝早會企喺欄邊聽下隻馬晨操跑過啲呼吸聲大唔大聲，去判斷隻馬呼吸好唔好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>蔣嘉琦BB：馬黃金期係咪4,5歲？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：多數係，但有啲短途馬會早熟啲，3歲已經黃金期，例如「幸福指數」。有啲長途馬會遲熟啲，到5,6歲先黃金期。同埋黃金期可能有兩次，有啲馬4,5歲黃金期喺咁贏，到6歲個季會表現回落，回完氣到7,8歲又有另一個高峰，最經典嘅例子係「極奇妙」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>球皇朗尼：想問下隻馬多汗代表咩？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：如果隻馬好淡定，無其他異樣，咁出汗可能只係因為天氣熱，應該無大影響。如果隻馬緊張 (例如條頸「登」到好直) or 發脾氣，咁出汗可能係情緒問題，唔係好現象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於馬匹狀態</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>HokYin：想問點睇馬狀態係好定差？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：如果係睇沙圈，個人經驗主要睇隻馬毛色深唔深，馬身夠唔夠壯，隻馬精唔精神。我其實係賽績派，睇狀態唔係我專長，只可以答到你咁多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於馬匹血統</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>黃金巨匠：對血統有無研究？鐘意邊匹Sire多？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：略有研究，啱啱睇馬個時好鐘意兩個父系，一個係Deputy Governor (代表作：多利高、真叻仔、飛象過河)，另一個係Snippets (代表作：活力先生、超級無敵)，呢兩個父系嘅馬性能廣泛，實而不華，印象中普遍身價唔高。而家我幾鐘意Castledale (代表作：天笑、牛精仔)，差唔多隻隻都識贏，實而不華，如果我做馬主會買呢個父系嘅馬，應該唔會好貴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於陰謀論 / 騎師</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Behrami：點睇潘頓成日拉馬？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：唔敢講佢係咪拉馬，但佢有時啲發揮係比較令人摸不著頭腦。印象中潘頓一時一日贏幾win，一時就全日無影，不妨睇下佢早段場次跑成點再諗諗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>綠豆爽：點睇柏寶？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：柏寶曾經係我嘅至愛，喺跑馬地日賽一日六Win實在令我好難忘，可惜個季差1 win輸左冠軍騎師比韋達之後就開始走下坡。柏寶而家跑馬經常無故提早移出2,3疊 (例如：慣性聆聽)，轉彎又經常過早發力同轉大彎，如果唔係超班馬 (例如：皇帝誥令) 實在好難蝕得起贏馬，難怪「幸運如意」都要飛起佢，買佢啲馬你要預左隻馬超班先好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Bergkamp：覺唔覺得梁家俊功架已經好過唔少洋將？包括杜利萊 李寶利 田泰安。</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：梁家俊係我最鐘意嘅華將，佢做見習騎師嗰時已經覺得佢與別不同，因為佢經常贏後上馬，例如：驍勇奔騰 同 夢幻飛駒 (我自己係受惠者，所以印象好深)，同其他見習騎師多數贏放頭馬好唔同。我同意你所講佢嘅功架已經好過唔少洋將，至少走位都好過佢地，最近贏「喜菜」係好例子，加上佢又夠硬功騎得，前途無可限量。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>小禁區王子：點睇布文？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：布文係而家澳洲最好個幾個騎師之一，我心目中佢係同潘頓同一個級數?騎師，如果長駐香港應該有頭四名。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於練馬師</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Jason.Chan：想知樓主對馬房部署有冇心得分享？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：坦白講，自己主要靠睇賽事片度馬，我係賽績/步速派，對馬房部署無花太多時間研究，只係對個別馬房嘅操練手法有啲認識，例如：約翰摩亞嘅參賽馬晨操無做最後試跑多數輸到前三名都無 (成日聽到評馬人子健提住，自己賽前有認真mark低，確實所言非虛)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>過咗紅海就係摩西：一直有啲疑問點解小方啲馬差唔多隻隻歪歪哋頸又幼（利申：只係我個人感覺，睇晨操片唔駛睇名都知果隻係佢），又成日踱兩圈就算唔鬼操但成績又唔錯。密跑當操真係咁掂當？定只係谷草對手真係弱弱哋？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：巴打，我都要利申先，除左初次出賽馬同自己心水馬，而家已經無睇晨操片，因為睇賽事片已經用左好多時間，自己唔係全職評馬人，根本無時間兼固咁多野，所以關於方仔啲馬點解條頸會奀奀地，我比唔到意見你，請見諒！<br />\n<br />\n至於佢啲馬密跑當操，我諗要留意一樣野係評分，因為啲馬唔密跑唔輸多幾場係減唔到分去有利水平，例如：「齊齊健康」今季29分贏馬，加到上35分，之後密跑輸幾場減番落30分又贏。另外，「雲呢拿」都係一個經典例子。方仔玩密跑玩評分真係出神入化。"},{"pid":"ff70d9335fe0559289815096d196c03bd68a835c","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:16:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於賽事形勢</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>伊布拉希莫維奇：想問下落雨+ c+3+慢步速放頭贏面係唔係最大？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：C+3+慢步速放頭贏面最大，如果加埋落雨要睇當時情況，有時內欄場地跑到爛晒，移出外欄嘅後上馬反而有利；有時跑之前已經停左雨，場地啜腳不利追，對放頭馬就有利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>伊布拉希莫維奇：壓完地果場其實對放頭馬最好？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：聽過有啲評馬人有咁嘅睇法，但我自己觀察唔係好覺。除非個日嘅場地特別利放，或者跑直路1000米，如果唔係利放定利追其實係應該視乎步速快定慢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>事勝意：你預計步速個時，會以同程同欄既時間做指標定係就咁同程時間? 因為有時同程同欄既時間比就咁同程時間有出入。</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：有少少睇唔明點解會關同程時間事，唔好意思，你係想問點預計個場馬步速快定慢？我主要會睇個場多唔多放頭馬，如果多放頭馬互燒，咁就較大機會係快步速，相反就較大機會係慢步速。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我會留意放頭馬係邊個騎師跑，見習騎師經驗淺同有磅減，加上較大機會各不相讓，佢地騎放頭馬較容易出現快步速；大師傅騎放頭馬就比較有分寸，遇到其他放頭馬會比較禮讓，未必會同你互燒，出現快步速嘅機會相對會較低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>觀星者：步速點決定？係賽前已知定賽後先知？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：步速快定慢通常同多唔多放頭馬有關，多放頭馬互相比壓力對方 (俗稱鬥燒)，咁就容易出現快步速；如果得一隻馬放，個騎師通常都會捉實隻馬，唔比佢走得咁快，咁就容易出現慢步速。<br />\n<br />\n步速喺賽前只係靠估，賽後就可以睇番分段時間判斷究竟係快步速定慢步速。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>觀星者：可唔可以講下前領/中置/後上馬嘅分別？同埋跑沙田1000米點解仲要搶內欄？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：前領係講緊放頭馬，最前嗰兩、三隻馬，前面無馬阻住佢地，望空跑嘅馬就係前領馬。另外有個講法係前置，前置馬就包括埋守係放頭馬後面4至6位嘅馬。<br />\n<br />\n中置通常係指守係第7至10位左右嘅馬，呢類馬靠追其實都可以叫後上馬。至於最後個幾隻馬通常叫大後上馬，因為佢地真係留到好後，主要靠喺最後直路後上追一段。<br />\n<br />\n至於直路1000米，要搞清楚，近住泥地跑道個邊條欄係內欄，近住看台呢邊條欄係外欄。啲馬跑直路1000米要搶埋外欄，因為外欄啲地靚啲，啲馬會跑得快啲。外欄啲地靚啲，因為比較少機會比馬踏到，你好少見啲馬跑轉彎路程入到最後直路會飛到出最外欄跑ga ma。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於賽制</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>朴初瓏：ching可唔可以講下分齡讓磅？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：巴打，你呢個問題問得好，好到實在太難答，因為分齡讓磅呢個制度實在太混亂，而馬會網頁嘅解釋又古靈精怪，如果我答錯煩請其他巴打指正<br />\n<br />\n根據馬會網頁講，北半球出生及南半球出生的兩歲馬(以十二月三十一日計算)在競逐讓賽時，可獲分齡讓磅五磅（如適用者）。(<a href=\"http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racinginfo/handicap_policy.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fracinginfo%2Fhandicap_policy.asp&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6d27b6b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racinginfo/handicap_policy.asp</a>)<br />\n<br />\n不過，你睇下嚟緊星期日跑嘅「佳運星」，佢明明係3歲北半球馬但都有5磅分齡讓磅減 (<a href=\"http://racing.hkjc.com/racing/info/meeting/Entries/chinese/Local/20170507/ST/Section/P50/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fracing.hkjc.com%2Fracing%2Finfo%2Fmeeting%2FEntries%2Fchinese%2FLocal%2F20170507%2FST%2FSection%2FP50%2F1&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=87d7cc43\" target=\"_blank\">http://racing.hkjc.com/racing/info/meeting/Entries/chinese/Local/20170507/ST/Section/P50/1</a>)<br />\n<br />\n我再拎「牛精叻仔」做例子，佢係北半球馬，第一季(13/14馬季)喺香港跑個時3歲，跑完新馬賽插入第三班，佢係有5磅分齡讓磅減，但當佢第二季(14/15馬季)再跑第三班，雖然仲係3歲但已經無左5磅分齡讓磅減<br />\n<br />\n再拎「祥勝愛駒」呢隻北半球2歲馬 (<a href=\"http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=L189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fracing%2FOtherHorse.asp%3FHorseNo%3DL189&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=262ea8d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/racing/OtherHorse.asp?HorseNo=L189</a>)做例子，我睇番佢第一季喺香港跑嗰時2歲，係有5磅分齡讓磅減；第二季喺香港跑開頭2歲，後尾3歲，佢全季都仲有5磅分齡讓磅減；去到第三季喺香港跑先無5磅分齡讓磅減。<br />\n<br />\n如果我無理解錯，咁北半球2歲馬係頭兩季喺香港跑都有5磅分齡讓磅減；而北半球3歲馬就頭一季喺香港跑先有5磅分齡讓磅減。<br />\n<br />\n至於南半球馬，3歲初出馬成日喺第四班都有，好似星期三晚跑嘅「常山耆寶」，唔見佢地有5磅分齡讓磅減，唔肯定南半球馬係咪要2歲第一季喺香港跑先有，實在無印象<br />\n<br />\n答得唔係幾好同肯定，唔好意思，希望有其他巴打指點下。<br />\n<br />\n智愛姆明：分齡讓磅 如果係每季既12月31日呢一日仲係2歲馬 成季就有分齡讓磅<br />\n北半球馬1月1轉歲<br />\n南半球馬8月1轉歲"},{"pid":"885f5bdbe638090ffe2c2afb64ce5a87f1c0e197","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於度馬</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>葉師父：自由哥想跟你學睇馬，你平時用幾多時間做功課？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：其實我主要係賽後做功課，每場馬都再睇番重播，細心睇番每隻馬跑成點，大約20分鐘一場，睇下有咩馬跑得好要mark低佢做跟進馬，所以我賽前唔係用太多時間做功課，好似唔超過兩個鐘，主要睇下有無自己嘅跟進馬跑，如果有就要研究下檔位、負磅、步速形勢、對手呢幾樣野佢有無著數。<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣留意有咩馬跑得好，我特別留意兩樣野：步速形勢有無利 同埋 係咪走第三疊。如果一隻馬遇到不利嘅步速形勢 / 走第三疊都跑得好，佢應該係評分仲有上升空間，呢啲馬我會mark低跟進。<br />\n<br />\n以今晚為例，「文藝學家」上場後上贏馬其實形勢好不利，因為步速好慢唔利追，結果佢都贏到，即係隻馬應該仲有分喺手，所以今晚負磅加左5磅都再贏，原本我都諗住貼佢做心水，不過預期賠率可能低過3倍，所以先無拎佢嚟做心水，估唔到最後有3.1倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於賽馬初哥</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>起個孖做爸爸：其實岩岩開始學玩馬仔係咪買下連贏位q三重彩就夠皮？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：獨贏 (Win)、位置 (Place)、連贏 (Q)同位置Q (PQ) 比較識合啱啱開始玩馬嘅朋友，因為佢地嘅玩法比較簡單。三重彩要順序跑入前三名，通常會用一啲投注策略買多幾隻馬，比較複雜，不妨遲少少再學。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>藍寶半全場：想學賭馬 應該點樣起手? 學馬 賽道 天氣 騎師 距離 步速既基本知識同玩法之外 仲有d 咩學? 點樣度馬？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：其實馬會有搞啲course比初學者認識賽馬，可去呢個網址：<a href=\"http://entertainment.hkjc.com/entertainment/chinese/learn-racing/racing-academy.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fentertainment.hkjc.com%2Fentertainment%2Fchinese%2Flearn-racing%2Fracing-academy.aspx&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a3891e17\" target=\"_blank\">http://entertainment.hkjc.com/entertainment/chinese/learn-racing/racing-academy.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n建議你先睇Racing 101，了解左香港賽馬嘅背景同基本知識。Racing 201會教你度馬，但程度會深好多，建議你睇左馬幾個月先再睇。<br />\n<br />\n至於度馬應該學咩先，我認為可視乎個人喜好，我自己最初係晨操派，成日睇收費電視每晚嘅晨操節目，後尾先再學睇賽績同步速。同埋建議你睇多啲賽馬節目，賽前節目同賽後節目都要睇，當然仲要睇埋賽馬直播。聽多啲評馬人嘅評論，雖然開頭未必明，但聽得多同自己睇多啲，慢慢就會愈明愈多。我自己以前成日睇方sir方駿暉，點睇賽績同步速都係喺佢到學番嚟。<br />\n<br />\n不過，我覺得睇賽績會易學少少，不妨先學睇隻馬嘅「6次近績」同「同程賽績」。介紹你用一個賽馬app叫Racing Touch，好適合初學者度馬用，可以喺呢到download：<a href=\"http://racingtouch.hkjc.com/ch/2017.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fracingtouch.hkjc.com%2Fch%2F2017.aspx&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fc0fc7b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://racingtouch.hkjc.com/ch/2017.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於投注</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>你仆街啦：平時賭得多唔多？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：唔多，只賭個日最有信心個1至2場，賭單場WP，平均注碼，無論贏輸都唔加注唔追數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>關於我條片用嘅app</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>A_Milik：想問下你個app叫咩名？</strong><br />\n<br />\n自由哥：馬會出嘅app叫Racing Touch，Android同iPad都可以用，可以喺呢條link download (<a href=\"http://racingtouch.hkjc.com/ch/2017.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fracingtouch.hkjc.com%2Fch%2F2017.aspx&d=EyFHVgn8L1AVuQtq1PSM5v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fc0fc7b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://racingtouch.hkjc.com/ch/2017.aspx</a>)。呢個app做得相當唔錯，本身個版面設計做得好靚，每隻馬啲評語同冷知識都寫得幾好，仲有賽事片可以睇番，仲可以投注同睇賽馬直播，集度馬、睇直播同投注於一身，相當方便好用。"},{"pid":"cc586f4f69ac0090fa725e808a47cde37f5e65c6","tid":323651,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"可以飛重心要次要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48488a6d16a6acef8930f9f4c892dc336a0a0d86","tid":323651,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"點睇R3? <br />\n自動波夠唔夠實力克服9檔?<br />\n勝利專家係唔係急於交待必要?"},{"pid":"9d14e1ded8131532d56bdcffc8797b22b7f02087","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以飛重心要次要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsad but ture<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4534cfbdecdc6fa407a0b953d38359c0b7dd37","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇R3? <br />\n自動波夠唔夠實力克服9檔?<br />\n勝利專家係唔係急於交待必要?</blockquote><br />\n入面快馬唔多，如果潘頓肯積極搶前，「自動波」應該克服到9檔。上次個第二賺晒慢步速，水準未必太高，但今次如果搶前有機會再賺。<br />\n<br />\n「勝利專家」咁快又出嚟跑應該係想快啲交待，最近呢兩個第二我覺得佢喺四班孭重磅唔突出，前次好辛苦先過到「好叻仔」，上次就輸比「佳運來」個幾馬位。<br />\n<br />\n今場我首選「開心健康」，今次跑番1400米，對手會比最近跑一哩個啲弱。今場快馬唔多，佢排1檔好大機會貼欄守3,4位賺形勢，馬膽我會揀佢。其餘拖番「自動波」、「勝利專家」同埋「好友益」。"},{"pid":"fea524968c815eb620766c878de56782cfde3322","tid":323651,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"講講頭場天狼星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fed30a279105247cb1c9859cf60b41f35946dcb","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講講頭場天狼星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢要靠輕磅放頭賺形勢先有機會贏，3次贏馬都係110磅或以下，孭到111磅至119磅最叻只係跑第二，今次孭到120磅佢無著數，就算比佢單騎領放賺形勢，我覺得最多都係跑3,4名。"},{"pid":"1ed5125bffe86f670a196376c6c610392e25f9d4","tid":323651,"uid":72396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"自由哥點睇漸信名駒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345604bca170876bb9793a434c60efa73092fb75","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由哥點睇漸信名駒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑草地證明唔多，我覺得佢會等泥地先郁手。"},{"pid":"6c28d7cc957ef21105fdf8fbb37c188d26023fd2","tid":323651,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"天下為攻點睇？"},{"pid":"8af744fe49f1b27efd296f4ec2c116f22fda417a","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天下為攻點睇？</blockquote><br />\n上場跑得差係因為搶口，同實力無關，睇佢前次喺四班孭重磅都輕鬆贏，喺三班無理由唔夠跑，今次換雷神應該會跑番出水準，呢隻係我首選。"},{"pid":"09b40e4d2222fcfe3c015638cb4901acde63122d","tid":323651,"uid":16220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"點睇r2 2 8 13<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b311d0771e7277ff4adce6ab239de2e424cc0931","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇r2 2 8 13<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「馬飛龍」我心水，今季喺四班同程跑第四輸個幾馬位，當時負125磅。今次降落五班重返同程，負磅竟然與當時一樣，但對手弱左好多，有贏面。<br />\n<br />\n「糖黐豆」沙田草地無贏過，明顯無泥地同跑馬地咁好，如果排外檔唔會怕佢，排內檔有邊線機會，跑出水準有前三名唔奇，可以拖埋。"},{"pid":"97737f4f1c25292baff027bb85e38b4bd43d5005","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"2 3 11點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a05412e742727c4235202c2f1b15a1460015ee","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"同埋r3 1 10"},{"pid":"ad5a03010485fbdedda17bf92876f9d9516010b8","tid":323651,"uid":31401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"真係中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ed5b4579e3dc0e539c59dd35befe831f19092a","tid":323651,"uid":43696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"點睇6,12"},{"pid":"4bd04dca79c1876cdaddc01b79f2bab6673a14f7","tid":323651,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"二中一原理<br />\n唔通燈到馬克羅斯無p?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aef49ad9d8c80262b0a1ae6a339b969ebd1564d","tid":323651,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"沈拿"},{"pid":"747bfbf5e2966bc5f02cb043e6d491546234daed","tid":323651,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"點睇第三場。10。  今飯碗"},{"pid":"92b924b542ced8725f947a31e7f8bbadac5ecde7","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二中一原理<br />\n唔通燈到馬克羅斯無p?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n二中一原理係以Win計ar ma，「馬克羅斯」應該會win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講番「馬飛龍」，無端端慢閘都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6df5ed1d0ca54e819fb55d69a686b47f069197c","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇第三場。10。  今飯碗</blockquote><br />\n「金飯碗」而家呢個負磅喺跑馬地無贏面，佢係五班頂、四班尾馬，不過今場對手實在太弱，我自己都有拖佢做腳。"},{"pid":"f25d64846a35f366471db64b3a91f59af8925b07","tid":323651,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"12號"},{"pid":"b91fa7c291c88f946acc022e5ba80c16c3e22d59","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋r3 1 10</blockquote><br />\n「常豐裕」之前喺同程蝕慢步速馬水準高，如果無跑累，佢跑出水準有機會再贏。<br />\n<br />\n「金飯碗」而家呢個負磅喺跑馬地無贏面，佢係五班頂、四班尾馬，不過今場對手實在太弱，我自己都有拖佢做腳。"},{"pid":"dcbaded2969fed2c2f8d0ae4caf16c2d3e29ee30","tid":323651,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12號</blockquote><br />\nGood?"},{"pid":"3ddb47756cd6329e9c5497068255be4cb683f6ef","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇6,12</blockquote><br />\n「幻影飛鷹」睇唔通，上場個第三水準一般，但佢之前缺課好耐，今次應該會更加好，我會拖埋佢。<br />\n<br />\n「心思熟慮」上場快放入直路無晒，今次多快放馬，佢好難跑，唔睇好。"},{"pid":"168be39a1d2f833c6d15b60cb7fdae467fe4e1c8","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12號</blockquote><br />\nGood?</blockquote><br />\n「心思熟慮」上場快放入直路無晒，今次多快放馬，佢好難跑，唔睇好。"},{"pid":"2829b63a04604a180d4afaf6ee2c4cfd8840e8f3","tid":323651,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"1,3,4,10"},{"pid":"8f3062d65c267fa2230267f74883648c7c037425","tid":323651,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"求第4場料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea179e03be51f56821f701821ebcf6c8440f551","tid":323651,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"4場盛勢拖永高 銀豐 自由哥點睇"},{"pid":"3084b114d36deb1e4c2adb2db64110c54ac44c59","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求第4場料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我首選「銀豐神駒」，今季喺四班同程贏「金錢路」一個馬位，佢喺四班係有少少超級。前次唔利追都追番第四唔差，上場唔知咩原因走樣，今次馬房last day唔會保留，跑番出水準佢實力最高。其餘拖埋「春盈」、「紅麗舍」、「盛勢」。"},{"pid":"9415a154ccd185eb682a65f50a9b2778052347fc","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4場盛勢拖永高 銀豐 自由哥點睇</blockquote><br />\n「盛勢」我會拖腳，上場贏五班賺左快步速唔算叻，升番上四班我覺得贏面唔高。<br />\n<br />\n「永高」喺四班成日近，排1檔有機會貼欄賺形勢，騎練今日成績好，可以拖。<br />\n<br />\n「銀豐神駒」係我首選，今季喺四班同程贏「金錢路」一個馬位，佢喺四班係有少少超級。前次唔利追都追番第四唔差，上場唔知咩原因走樣，今次馬房last day唔會保留，跑番出水準佢實力最高。"},{"pid":"c899b2b17548c0e172af5c6aaa35fc89472969c8","tid":323651,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"大雨 亂局爆冷？"},{"pid":"3c6f5bdfdc63ec2aeddae2b2226b4fe10be420de","tid":323651,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T05:59:24.000Z","msg":"隻1p有4倍 抵博"},{"pid":"676870ddc08ae116c5cdea3bd39eb0be398e8cf4","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大雨 亂局爆冷？</blockquote><br />\n唔出奇，有啲冷門可能跑濕地好叻但大家唔知。"},{"pid":"6ce2d8c0693e4a073e814d72ce8cd4e2c8b27838","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"R5 4 5 7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1f0a9a5fa30aeda8c6144d5fb1844fff5bdd7f","tid":323651,"uid":61015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:05:24.000Z","msg":"已經連輸四場 想針"},{"pid":"640e163c26c809172c768c85da626124bfd14b48","tid":323651,"uid":126506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4場盛勢拖永高 銀豐 自由哥點睇</blockquote><br />\n「盛勢」我會拖腳，上場贏五班賺左快步速唔算叻，升番上四班我覺得贏面唔高。<br />\n<br />\n「永高」喺四班成日近，排1檔有機會貼欄賺形勢，騎練今日成績好，可以拖。<br />\n<br />\n「銀豐神駒」係我首選，今季喺四班同程贏「金錢路」一個馬位，佢喺四班係有少少超級。前次唔利追都追番第四唔差，上場唔知咩原因走樣，今次馬房last day唔會保留，跑番出水準佢實力最高。</blockquote><br />\n利害"},{"pid":"4dfc72da87f69eb562f2fc7dea1c793fe8c8870c","tid":323651,"uid":126506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"5場點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a9f743fe0f72840ff120b9110357dac1354b23","tid":323651,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"精壯神駿？"},{"pid":"5a91884b47631ceff133127490f939f3651d8de1","tid":323651,"uid":31401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"自由哥破左2場重心魔咒未？"},{"pid":"833a32fd08f32e56d1a9cda92976feabbfcc1a9a","tid":323651,"uid":43696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:11:44.000Z","msg":"點睇友瑩采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8dc67ea29a041a48ff4af587267842a766e907","tid":323651,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"爺爺膽 拖寶正寶 幸運7星 自由哥點睇"},{"pid":"5259eb35ed84ccd8201ed22e24b62616a1a4911d","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由哥破左2場重心魔咒未？</blockquote><br />\n未，「馬克羅斯」Win得，「喜旺寶」濕地唔掂，馬主之前訪問講過，外地最差個場就係跑濕地。"},{"pid":"61d6db3650153bea4d5e320f2a750534bda335ca","tid":323651,"uid":67264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"自由哥多謝 我默默地跟左銀豐位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e89575bbab795491c57408d9a53ca69eee443a","tid":323651,"uid":16661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"今場買8-5-11點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f01b389a7174dd9c6e28937eabcab51c52fa67","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>R5 4 5 7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢三隻都唔係我頭四選，呢場好平均，好多馬可以揀，仲要落埋雨，難玩。<br />\n<br />\n「寶正寶」兩場贏馬都係賺慢步速贏少少，水準唔算高，夾埋加左11磅，我唔信佢仲有得贏。<br />\n<br />\n「勁豐裕」表現飄忽，佢喺四班贏馬都係孭122磅或以上，128磅佢無乜贏面，而家係靠雷神幫手跑高啲。<br />\n<br />\n「醉必勝」今季孭127磅贏同程，今次孭126磅有條件跑得好，三隻之中我比較鐘意呢隻。"},{"pid":"47e82cd390889f63f78582730e2108e76774fc0b","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5場點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我首選「友瑩采」，上場喺五班贏三個馬位，上番四班應該仲有贏面，如果排內檔我已經拍左片做全日心水，排外檔信心打折扣，但我都係決定揀佢先。其餘會揀埋「精壯神駿」、「其樂無窮」、「蒜頭爺爺」。呢場好平均，其實仲有唔少馬可以拖，難玩。"},{"pid":"c1a8688aa33b49eca540158a0f20e590266ed7bb","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇友瑩采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我首選「友瑩采」，上場喺五班贏三個馬位，上番四班應該仲有贏面，如果排內檔我已經拍左片做全日心水，排外檔信心打折扣，但我都係決定揀佢先。"},{"pid":"9c27c076c3043483a1327694c2e7f1665dcdfc35","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精壯神駿？</blockquote><br />\n三班跑第四個場全程走三疊都近，落到四班隨時贏得，問題係佢跑唔跑得出水準，呢樣要摶。"},{"pid":"d9bded544fdf70fd4866fcb8dfc8aed49c2a07bc","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"sorry其他答唔切。"},{"pid":"641384f0347aa0dfc3858cb87f2e7c4b2275e515","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"自由哥想問下何良馬房點睇 家父長追佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a5d650ccddc49dcc814caf8d57d4230199b2f5","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由哥想問下何良馬房點睇 家父長追佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無研究馬房，印象中佢一係全日出擊，一係全日無影。"},{"pid":"261bc74951cb9ec21388054d10c7b5fa2a3ed4be","tid":323651,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"請問自由哥點睇6埸喜歡盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢場你會揀咩馬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58795a1c2584eeb0cd5d6261984b797c5f42497b","tid":323651,"uid":61015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"r6 2,5,6點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae14ab1470bd97bb4d47ec1b126407326334500","tid":323651,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"開心健康拖 八心 好叻仔 點睇"},{"pid":"c117d59a0e0cbe81ab7ee87aa4c89b5d9b631bfb","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:52:15.000Z","msg":"覺得14有無機會入p"},{"pid":"5a73485e77149a9e3940712de07595daf2a6729d","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問自由哥點睇6埸喜歡盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢場你會揀咩馬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上場個第五連「勁飛寶寶」都跑唔贏，我覺得水準馬馬，不過呢隻馬樣同腳法唔差，長線可以留意，今次增程跑1400米我會留意佢跑成點。<br />\n<br />\n今場無馬突出唔易玩，原本首選「開心健康」，而家首選揀「自動波」，上場個第二其實賺左慢步速未必太叻，不過今次排9檔入面快馬唔多，有機會跟前守3,4位再賺，用埋潘頓戰意唔駛懷疑。其餘拖埋「勝利專家」、「好友益」、「慷慨寶」。"},{"pid":"f0e92e55c6f2ee9f82e4c0cd6c59a78eb04c3100","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>r6 2,5,6點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「八心之煌」以往跑1400米無快步速好易搶口，今場睇落唔會快，驚佢留得辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n「好友益」四班要對手失準先有機會贏，但佢忠心成日都追一段，有位置機會。"},{"pid":"136f833c808bed08885763d6c145fcc846f4e71e","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心健康拖 八心 好叻仔 點睇</blockquote><br />\n「八心之煌」以往跑1400米無快步速好易搶口，今場睇落唔會快，驚佢留得辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n「好叻仔」體弱馬季初頭幾鋪最好，而家已經非最佳時，變數係雷神騎睇下幫到幾多，如果跑出近仗水準佢都係跑位置居多。"},{"pid":"d8bd671d4f3c8ad2bef71505b830ff7f9e27a648","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得14有無機會入p</blockquote><br />\n今次變數係個體重終於回升番，賽績唔會有野睇，我頭四隻揀唔到佢。"},{"pid":"e47bb0c7d068800103783257590cb18e33840e04","tid":323651,"uid":25417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請問自由哥點睇6埸喜歡盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢場你會揀咩馬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上場個第五連「勁飛寶寶」都跑唔贏，我覺得水準馬馬，不過呢隻馬樣同腳法唔差，長線可以留意，今次增程跑1400米我會留意佢跑成點。<br />\n<br />\n今場無馬突出唔易玩，原本首選「開心健康」，而家首選揀「自動波」，上場個第二其實賺左慢步速未必太叻，不過今次排9檔入面快馬唔多，有機會跟前守3,4位再賺，用埋潘頓戰意唔駛懷疑。其餘拖埋「勝利專家」、「好友益」、「慷慨寶」。</blockquote><br />\n4隻返曬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2d4225f4d9ca10c93e376544ffb7936dc54684","tid":323651,"uid":61450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"自由哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dcc274ba4f4de9d4a0972f8312090e795e6fc1","tid":323651,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"勢必跑？"},{"pid":"a044c4cabcef12b89bbf4b8570641b0c95af3a07","tid":323651,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:17:59.000Z","msg":"贏風雲點睇"},{"pid":"a6b88067f8dfc87c833e75105d5eafccf751c878","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勢必跑？</blockquote><br />\n今季贏一班同程，佢喺三班有啲超級，不過今場無乜放頭馬似乎步速會慢，驚佢追唔切，同埋落完雨場地會啜腳唔利追，我自己四選揀唔到。"},{"pid":"92a676b58602c6f7f3e4a016b5ec3c8b58dd4a13","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>贏風雲點睇</blockquote><br />\n今季兩次喺同程跑第二都係賺左快步速，今場睇落無乜放頭馬，步速可能會慢，未必啱佢追，場地落過雨會啜腳亦未必利追。"},{"pid":"2c6bc4e9a7f40a47bd1edfc9ae2a80b9f2425dd7","tid":323651,"uid":60080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"鈦金剛 琪麒穎 q?"},{"pid":"d9acf93b3a42593e050479361d920a31242b0258","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鈦金剛 琪麒穎 q?</blockquote><br />\n「鈦金剛」睇呢幾場似乎跑唔番，變數係換左雷神，如果你信騎師可以要埋。<br />\n<br />\n「琪麒穎」用蔣嘉琦應該會放 or 中段發力放頭，佢有機會賺步速同場地形勢，呢隻有位置機會。"},{"pid":"151978d2c01b3232378228489965e4a05533c41a","tid":323651,"uid":88887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"8場1號點睇"},{"pid":"d3cda13a402b02d76bd128114a45f649d73a2b91","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8場1號點睇</blockquote><br />\n我第四選，今季贏過兩次三級賽，馬有級數，但1800米好過1600米，同埋孭頂磅要讓個三強唔少磅，未必讓得起。"},{"pid":"8d98e0ffd569f5b538f94a4dc6ebdbdccfb67493","tid":323651,"uid":4215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"呢場有無心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157c41a37cdcaf45cf2c87b15709a573f3460bc7","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢場有無心水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇第一頁。"},{"pid":"d8f42710fcd010f0201279fd122cebe9d1826b64","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"兩隻只能活一隻仍然生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7b86842b100782ba0e9823471e652c0dc0061e","tid":323651,"uid":6144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"4 6q 如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad6b9e721b69789308e591c3fb33e555b4e5064","tid":323651,"uid":52355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"點睇11"},{"pid":"b66905142a0d9d3dec0e18d929a20371f3820aec","tid":323651,"uid":4215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"好波自由哥 翻身了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d15fef4ab1ebfd493e9cf4f0d8c6a1d1d393484","tid":323651,"uid":79008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"自由哥好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efebe9b3a5e814787843d396d2d9200bf4f70a39","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4 6q 如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「好加加」係退步緊嘅馬，而家一擺唔到係前面就多數跑得唔好，跑1400米驚佢早段唔夠快，考騎師功力。<br />\n<br />\n「世界紀錄」原本係我首選，但場地唔係咁利追，佢而家經常都留到好後，形勢唔著數，位置機會較高。"},{"pid":"669908f26422bb65774fad5e941d1d046264bdc9","tid":323651,"uid":8619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"請問呢場首選係咩"},{"pid":"07dcae8e6a4e19ed1238c4b63d580dfd0441384e","tid":323651,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"2 7 12 點睇"},{"pid":"6761e97db4fa127a533d6c65b9cd67661d116224","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇11</blockquote><br />\n「估惑」外地贏1600米，睇腳法似均速中長途馬，今次跑1400米應該會放頭，有機會賺場地利放形勢，有位置機會，贏我就有保留，始於呢啲3歲北半球喺香港第一次跑要贏難度頗高。"},{"pid":"def17ec30a25aa1074e1b242b61e31493f7b8812","tid":323651,"uid":66115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"自由哥指點下之後幾場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b96215d3226ddf07caddd9eabb4dfdf33e6f32e","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問呢場首選係咩</blockquote><br />\n我首選「威力名城」，之前喺同程輸比「蒙古王」水準應該ok，今場排2檔有機會跟前守3,4位賺場地利前置形勢。其餘拖番「世界紀錄」、「中華之光」、「估惑」。"},{"pid":"ee1fbce96777db0b5aa41ce7eba2ecdbc33af3a4","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2 7 12 點睇</blockquote><br />\n「中華之光」上場無跑錯但表現失望，可能前次贏「君悅灣」水準唔係太高，我會拖埋佢因為前次贏過濕地。<br />\n<br />\n我首選「威力名城」，之前喺同程輸比「蒙古王」水準應該ok，今場排2檔有機會跟前守3,4位賺場地利前置形勢。<br />\n<br />\n「日威夜威」排外檔留後跑經常追唔切，場地又唔利追，如果揀後上馬我寧願要「世界紀錄」。"},{"pid":"072fd37e8f025a3eac4ba5cc075d5400df132d26","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由哥指點下之後幾場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a133b9a657c4f96d7830da13ee7187c22d9ce93e","tid":323651,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4 6q 如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「好加加」係退步緊嘅馬，而家一擺唔到係前面就多數跑得唔好，跑1400米驚佢早段唔夠快，考騎師功力。<br />\n<br />\n「世界紀錄」原本係我首選，但場地唔係咁利追，佢而家經常都留到好後，形勢唔著數，位置機會較高。</blockquote><br />\n希望世界紀錄會跟返前<br />\n上場賽後報告麥偉利原本都諗住跟前<br />\n但騎落驚唔夠快縮後左"},{"pid":"921bc3a2820ac786b58455d54cf63888660d11f6","tid":323651,"uid":66115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"自由哥，10場1搭9點睇"},{"pid":"fef90b28062ba419fd0dae29c82f3f29a25fcdfe","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自由哥，10場1搭9點睇</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻係我第3,4選。「劍無名」上場蝕慢步速追上嚟跑第二，水準唔錯，馬明顯跑起左狀態，排6檔形勢同上次差唔多，應該會跟前守2至4位，有機會再跑得好。<br />\n<br />\n「旅遊拿督」跑落唔係好超級，但前次濕地跑過第二，加埋又有內檔幫手，佢有機會再跑入前三名。"},{"pid":"6d5d3ac8009903617eca2b9f1e71d6d249d4b981","tid":323651,"uid":66115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自由哥，10場1搭9點睇</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻係我第3,4選。「劍無名」上場蝕慢步速追上嚟跑第二，水準唔錯，馬明顯跑起左狀態，排6檔形勢同上次差唔多，應該會跟前守2至4位，有機會再跑得好。<br />\n<br />\n「旅遊拿督」跑落唔係好超級，但前次濕地跑過第二，加埋又有內檔幫手，佢有機會再跑入前三名。</blockquote><br />\n首次選係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84065d6cfef6fb878540e916202d68900e8ee8bf","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自由哥，10場1搭9點睇</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻係我第3,4選。「劍無名」上場蝕慢步速追上嚟跑第二，水準唔錯，馬明顯跑起左狀態，排6檔形勢同上次差唔多，應該會跟前守2至4位，有機會再跑得好。<br />\n<br />\n「旅遊拿督」跑落唔係好超級，但前次濕地跑過第二，加埋又有內檔幫手，佢有機會再跑入前三名。</blockquote><br />\n首次選係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首選「天下為攻」，前次喺四班同程孭重磅輕鬆贏，我信佢係超級馬，三班攔佢唔住。上場跑得差係輸在搶口，同實力無關，今次換雷神應該會跑番出水準。<br />\n<br />\n次選原本係「快利」，但啱啱發脾氣撞埋條欄到，要再睇睇先。計實力佢上場喺四班同程孭重磅贏個幾馬位，後生馬仲進步緊，升上三班孭輕磅應該都夠跑。"},{"pid":"eef071a5ea42a213da2b6eb381cf18151a80c77a","tid":323651,"uid":126506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自由哥，10場1搭9點睇</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻係我第3,4選。「劍無名」上場蝕慢步速追上嚟跑第二，水準唔錯，馬明顯跑起左狀態，排6檔形勢同上次差唔多，應該會跟前守2至4位，有機會再跑得好。<br />\n<br />\n「旅遊拿督」跑落唔係好超級，但前次濕地跑過第二，加埋又有內檔幫手，佢有機會再跑入前三名。</blockquote><br />\n首次選係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首選「天下為攻」，前次喺四班同程孭重磅輕鬆贏，我信佢係超級馬，三班攔佢唔住。上場跑得差係輸在搶口，同實力無關，今次換雷神應該會跑番出水準。<br />\n<br />\n次選原本係「快利」，但啱啱發脾氣撞埋條欄到，要再睇睇先。計實力佢上場喺四班同程孭重磅贏個幾馬位，後生馬仲進步緊，升上三班孭輕磅應該都夠跑。</blockquote><br />\n快利發脾氣到大慢閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8337b8bd26d07e8d7d2d0227c9d43630d954b1f9","tid":323651,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"請問自由哥尾場比卡超有無機會呢<br />\n之前幾場都無咩點騎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蒙古王今日場地追唔追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尾場你會揀咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6557b8a72dff4c0a07bba2d889960912ef4d9c","tid":323651,"uid":64252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:29:27.000Z","msg":"尾場tips!"},{"pid":"2ba53769de6def1ca0adbcec56996de6e8504f19","tid":323651,"uid":113075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問自由哥尾場比卡超有無機會呢<br />\n之前幾場都無咩點騎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蒙古王今日場地追唔追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尾場你會揀咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尾場好難玩，我覺得1,2,4,6,7,10,12,14都有前三名機會，量力而為。<br />\n<br />\n我首選博左「彩福」，之前喺一班同程贏過「加州議長」同「永旺年年」，計級數佢數一數二。最近幾場唔係走去放頭就係全程走三疊，跑得差唔駛計數，今次排4檔應該會走二疊守3,4位，如果識跑濕地有機會橫掃。<br />\n<br />\n次選「太陽喜喜」，佢跑開1600同1800米啲對手較強，跑1400米佢贏級數，如果13檔可能會放頭，有機會賺埋場地利前置形勢。<br />\n<br />\n再揀要「龍船」，最近兩場輸比超級馬「馬克羅斯」雖敗猶榮，縮程跑1400米佢一樣應付到，排3檔可以跟前守3,4位好跑。<br />\n<br />\n最後揀埋「蒙古王」，佢二班未必夠贏，但1400米佢確實好叻，上次慢閘都追番一段上嚟跑第三，唔拖埋唔得。"}]}